Fahmida Mahbub
pizza dough ta temon kisu na

Add 1 tsp yeast to half cup luke warm water..to activate it...set it for around 10 mins, ull see foamy stuff on surface. then add to it 1 tbsp sugar, half tsp salt, 1 tbsp oil. Add this to 1 cup flour, add a little more flour if needed. then let mix. ull get a sticky dough. let it rest till it rises... then add a little flour and knead a little bit.
